<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Country Hills Village</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A newly established multifamily neighborhood located on the northeastern side of the community of Country Hills, Country Hills Village has been developed in the last ten years or so.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Apart from its close proximity to the Country Hills Towne Centre that offers a variety of shopping options for the residents, the Country Hills Village also houses the multifunctional recreational giant Cardel Place that boasts of a number of swimming pools, libraries, exercise rooms, sports fields and what not.</p>
